      "value": "<p>You fill the area with assailing winds, which continue to whip at creatures long after the spell ends. You deal 12d4 wind damage to each creature in the area, and each creature in the area must make a Fortitude save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, and takes an additional @Damage[(2*(ceil(@item.level/2)-2))d4[persistent,wind-ff]] damage</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature takes double both the initial and persistent damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The damage increases by 2d4, and the persistent damage increases by 2d4.</p>"
